食飯或者去玩都有叫埋嗰啲女仔朋友 但係冇講我知佢哋有去 我亦都唔識嗰啲女仔<br />\n本身自己迷信 走咗去占卜睇相嗰啲<br />\n一睇佢果然講中我同我男朋友好多嘢<br />\n我真係好鍾意佢 <br />\n但係佢就話我男朋友只會愛埋我今年<br />\n之後我哋就會分手<br />\n<br />\n我依家同佢相處盡量當係好朋友咁<br />\n呢一刻開心就夠  之後佢同朋友去 邊做緊咩 都唔過問太多<br />\n希望放鬆吓自己 因為成日偷偷地Check住佢好大壓力 <br />\n如果真係淨翻今年呢幾個月 <br />\n我係咪真係好好咁享受佢仲鍾意我嘅呢幾個月好？<br />\n<br />\n其實有冇人試過占卜睇相 同現實會相反<br />\n唉雙魚座女仔真係太多愁善感"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T15:45:13.000Z","msg":"你都shot撚左<br />\n佢見你女仔去得都知9成感情有問題先搵佢<br />\n人地9up幾句你就信 真係on99"},{"pid":"b9991b51b7ce0a4fba1c01bfdf1ac33b1a99aa44","tid":2245852,"uid":336731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"d雙魚座好鍾意講自己多愁善感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6730d10ddfa575b2ac2521502328f1af1829fd3","tid":2245852,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T15:45:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9557296c7cb0ed29e4b184fcbc95b0659da688de","tid":2245852,"uid":260328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"要幾撚on9先會信星座 占卜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434c9198bfcb8db70980705d6286b776d4985f5c","tid":2245852,"uid":18040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T15:54:01.000Z","msg":"快撚d分"},{"pid":"ddad9d6f8a09b7809e01e61661db4989da12480b","tid":2245852,"uid":65275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T15:54:58.000Z","msg":"屌你真係戇鳩架喎"},{"pid":"aa7bcf2d004f2a1c9148ece238495c9319ee0ef8","tid":2245852,"uid":242244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T15:55:14.000Z","msg":"既然知道要分手，仲等咩，早分可以早d搵過第個水魚"},{"pid":"637befa11b5c4bae963ff3ae89a68f6fa12611fb","tid":2245852,"uid":327858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"你聽完占卜之後自然會跟住佢講嘅方向咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好咁蠢啦"},{"pid":"ad3e9cae84f74c1245d94b951ba9a771826f2ec5","tid":2245852,"uid":322309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ac1f1b54e148529118dfd8c0c4996df1e0a4b20","tid":2245852,"uid":248275,"like":5,"dislike":25,"score":-20,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"兒登仔鐘意點都屌左人先<br />\n絲打唔好放喺心上<br />\n我諗一係好好享受完然後你自己改變左先<br />\n一係就搵埋啲占卜店通常有埋嘅靈氣幫幫手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:18:29.000Z","msg":"靈氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4d6f0d1676b501c6e0a01a5d973eac03f95a0e","tid":2245852,"uid":11301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:23:28.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af48d58e46a9c1dbbea2d669407f3a9614c06b1b","tid":2245852,"uid":247471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:29:43.000Z","msg":"咁煩拍嚟做乜"},{"pid":"c844e6ffdede98f9ee4bcff3ac45be54b65aa73e","tid":2245852,"uid":306000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我仲以為你地是但一個有咗cancer要死<br />\n<br />\n無論占卜與否<br />\n其實齋睇妳嘅感情描述都知道段關係本身危危地<br />\n我個人認為占卜佬都只係睇妳感情現況再比啲類似預知未來嘅建議等佢可以收妳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身相處唔開心 + 對方隱瞞自己同異性出街<br />\n<br />\n其實妳仲同佢一齊做咩？<br />\n妳而家想做嘅係修補關係？定放棄？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想修補關係嘅話，唔係應該首先兩個人坐低認真溝通下段關係有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果妳係咁重視占卜佬講嘅結果，<br />\n（我個人認為=比佢嘅說話綑綁住）<br />\n其實妳而家放棄就可以，<br />\n何必繼續落去？<br />\n睇住心愛嘅人離開自己係好折磨嘅事<br />\n<br />\n如果妳仲想試下，<br />\n唔甘心就咁就散，<br />\n我建議妳真係再試下，<br />\n真係做啲野去修補返段關係"},{"pid":"0b4874722feb2810651a54ebac237ce207ca3138","tid":2245852,"uid":148378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9ea45b1fcf3a513f8caa44ec33f1ffc2f3a3992","tid":2245852,"uid":43842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:58:36.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦 講乜你就信架啦 係咪on9架<br />\n同一個卦 唔同人有唔同解釋方法<br />\n更重要係占卜唔係要你接受未來現實 而係趁而家改變未來<br />\n<br />\n我唔知你係咪命定論既人 但我可以同你講你自己命運有得自己改變<br />\n<br />\n利申: 識少少風水 只會同熟人起卦"},{"pid":"4226884d9d1f7e22a1b035578f3aa80b69205571","tid":2245852,"uid":68813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T17:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b04e40f21fa39d86a813c46d6bca402fed1049","tid":2245852,"uid":87313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}